history.proof: intros n m p H1 H2. hauto lq: on rew: off use: Zmult_ge_neg_compat_l, Z.gt_lt_iff, Z.le_neq, Z.ge_le_iff, Z.mul_reg_l unfold: Z.lt, Z.ge, Z_dec.

ctx: intros n m p H1 H2.
exceptions.tactic: apply Z.le_trans with (m := Z.mul p n); auto.
exceptions.exn: In environment n, m, p : Z H1 : 0 > p H2 : n >= m Unable to unify "(?M1415 ?= ?M1417) = Gt" with "(m ?= n) = Lt".

original: intros n m p H1 H2. apply Zmult_ge_compat_l_rev in H2. apply Z.le_trans with (m := Z.mul p n); auto.
